<div>
  <div>
    <h1>
      Welcome to the Travel Credit Card Optimizer!    </h1>
  </div>
  Today, many credit cards offer benefits in the form of travel credits. Which one will get YOU the biggest benefit?
  </div>
  <div> 
  Put in a typical month's expenses and let AI do the rest!
</div>

<div>
  <div>
    <h3>
      Start a new conversation with ChatGPT to get the most rewards!
    </h2>

    <form action="/insert_conversation" method="post">
    <button class="fancy-button">Start conversation
    </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>
<div>
  <div>
    <table border="1">
      <tr>
        <th>
          ID
        </th>

        <th>
          User
        </th>

        <th>
          Created at
        </th>

        <th>
          Updated at
        </th>

        <th>
        </th>
      </tr>

      <% @list_of_conversations.each do |a_conversation| %>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <%= a_conversation.id %>
        </td>

        <td>
          <%= a_conversation.user_id %>
        </td>

        <td>
          <%= time_ago_in_words(a_conversation.created_at) %> ago
        </td>
        <td>
          <%= time_ago_in_words(a_conversation.updated_at) %> ago
        </td>

        <td>
          <a href="/conversations/<%= a_conversation.id %>">
            Show details
          </a>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <% end %>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>
